text: Besaka alaha ne bahuta sare mauki'am upara tuhadi madada kiti hai ate hunaina de dina vi jadom' tuhanu bahuginati de hakara ne cura kara dita si. Phira uha (bahuginati) tuhade kujha vi kama na a'i. Ate dharati apani visalata tom ba'ada vi tuhade la'i sauri ho ga'i. Phira tusim pitha dikha ke bhaja nikale
